able fall from the 22 golds won in Japan in 2021.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9857051590815418, \"rank\": 0.01249801184772585, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold count\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"a big drop\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"a noticeable fall\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the 22 golds\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 100 days to go from Paris, the British team is far from being finalised for the summer Games but the 66 medals are expected to come from 22 sports in all, with Britain tipped for the third-highest medal tally of all the nations.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999988117452, \"rank\": 1.188118204574617e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9814417012070549, \"rank\": 0.017872327938874492, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.93570649874922, \"rank\": 0.06871108932123662, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}